sql_query.sql: SELECT "group_users"."group_id" FROM "group_users" WHERE "group_users"."group_id" IN (SELECT "groups"."id" FROM "groups" WHERE (groups.id > 0) AND "groups"."automatic" = TRUE ORDER BY name ASC) AND "group_users"."user_id" = 1815

SELECT "group_users"."group_id" FROM "group_users" WHERE "group_users"."group_id" IN (SELECT "groups"."id" FROM "groups" WHERE (groups.id > 0) AND "groups"."automatic" = TRUE ORDER BY name ASC) AND "group_users"."user_id" = 1815 AND "group_users"."owner" = TRUE
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "groups" WHERE (groups.id > 0) AND "groups"."automatic" = TRUE

SELECT "groups"."id", "groups"."name", "groups"."created_at", "groups"."updated_at", "groups"."automatic", "groups"."user_count", "groups"."automatic_membership_email_domains", "groups"."primary_group", "groups"."title", "groups"."grant_trust_level", "groups"."incoming_email", "groups"."has_messages", "groups"."flair_bg_color", "groups"."flair_color", "groups"."bio_raw", "groups"."bio_cooked", "groups"."allow_membership_requests", "groups"."full_name", "groups"."default_notification_level", "groups"."visibility_level", "groups"."public_exit", "groups"."public_admission", "groups"."membership_request_template", "groups"."messageable_level", "groups"."mentionable_level", "groups"."publish_read_state", "groups"."members_visibility_level", "groups"."flair_icon", "groups"."flair_upload_id" FROM "groups" WHERE (groups.id > 0) AND "groups"."automatic" = TRUE ORDER BY name ASC LIMIT 36 OFFSET 0
